CommonFields.Publication: IEEE Transactions on Dielectrics and Electrical Insulation
CommonFields.Title: Mechanisms leading to nonlinear electrical response of a nano p-SiC/silicone rubber composite
CommonFields.Author: Wang, X.
Nelson, J. K.
Schadler, L. S.
Hillborg, H.
CommonFields.Location: Rensselaer Polytechnic Institute, Troy, NY, USA

Mixing.Description: composites were prepared by mixing nano-SiC powder with silicone resin in a Hauschild high speed mixer

Additive.Description: Used as the silicone rubber crosslinking agent

Drying-Evaporation.Description: samples were kept in vacuum oven overnight to remove any dicumyl peroxide residue

ChooseParameter.Other: gold electrodes (2 cm diameter) were sputter deposited onto both surfaces of sample discs

Electrometry.Description: biased with a Bertan 10 kV voltage source
